#. type: Plain text
#: origin/heimdal.txt:308
msgid ""
"Issuing \"make check\" will run an extensive test suite on the build. My "
"experience is negative however, as way deep into the tests, it sometimes "
"would fail during the \"xnlock\" test. The \"xnlock\" program is a stupid "
"little locking screen saver (secure, though, when it transmits the unlocking "
